@startuml
' Diagram: F09 - Theo doi khach hang va trang thai su dung (Sequence)
' Status: VERIFIED
' Baseline: HEAD 8ca9ec7
' Source:
' - VinhKhanhTour.CMS/Pages/BanDo/Index.cshtml.cs: OnGetAsync(), LoadSubscriptionsPortableAsync(), LoadLocationsPortableAsync(), LoadPoiActivityCountsAsync(), BuildCustomerRows(), ApplySearch(), ApplyFilter(), ApplySort()
' - VinhKhanhTour.CMS/Pages/BanDo/Index.cshtml
' - VinhKhanhTour.API/Data/AppDbContext.cs
' Note: Sequence cap nhat theo BanDo hien tai: render server-side, helper portable EF la luong chinh; raw helper van ton tai trong file nhung khong phai path chinh.
' Note: Sequence khong liet ke cau SQL; chi the hien owner method cua IndexModel va thao tac persistence chinh.
title F09 - Theo doi khach hang va trang thai su dung

actor Admin
control "BanDo IndexModel" as IndexModel
participant "AppDbContext\n<<persistence>>" as DbContext
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

Admin -> IndexModel: OnGetAsync(search, filter, sort, dir)
IndexModel -> IndexModel: NormalizeOption(filter/sort)\nSortDir\nnow, onlineCutoff, expiringSoonCutoff

IndexModel -> IndexModel: LoadSubscriptionsPortableAsync()
IndexModel -> DbContext: ToListAsync()
DbContext -> DB: read grouped DangKyApps
DB --> DbContext: rows
DbContext --> IndexModel: DeviceSubscription[]

IndexModel -> IndexModel: LoadLocationsPortableAsync()
IndexModel -> DbContext: ToListAsync()
DbContext -> DB: read valid VitriKhachs
DB --> DbContext: rows
DbContext --> IndexModel: DeviceLocation[]

IndexModel -> IndexModel: LoadPoiActivityCountsAsync(VisitedSourceValues)
IndexModel -> DbContext: ToListAsync()
DbContext -> DB: read grouped visited POI counts
DB --> DbContext: rows
DbContext --> IndexModel: DevicePoiCount[]

IndexModel -> IndexModel: LoadPoiActivityCountsAsync(ViewedSourceValues)
IndexModel -> DbContext: ToListAsync()
DbContext -> DB: read grouped viewed POI counts
DB --> DbContext: rows
DbContext --> IndexModel: DevicePoiCount[]

IndexModel -> IndexModel: BuildCustomerRows()
note right of IndexModel
  BuildCustomerRows() derives:
  expiresAt, currentPoi, isOnline,
  viewedCount, visitedCount,
  experiencePoints and level.
end note
IndexModel -> IndexModel: ApplySearch()\nApplyFilter()\nApplySort()
IndexModel --> Admin: render customer table + summary tiles
@enduml
